eveal the establishment of the accretion disk in this system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Jun 2017 04:51:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 Jul 2017 07:07:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-26"}
